Functions:
=========
bpca.default         Biplot for \code{data.frame} or \code{matrix} objects.
bpca.prcomp          Biplot for \code{prcomp} objects.
bpca                 Main function (S3 based).
dt.tools             Calculates vector variable lengths, angles between vector
                     variables and variable correlations from \code{data.frame}
                     or \code{matrix} objects.
plot.bpca.2d         Plots \code{bpca.2d} objects with \pkg{graphics}.
plot.bpca.3d         Plots \code{bpca.3d} objects with \pkg{scatterplot3d}
                     (\pkg{graphics}-based) and \pkg{rgl} (OpenGL based).
plot.qbpca           Plots \code{qbpca} objects with \pkg{graphics}.

print.xtable         Generic print method for \code{xtable} objects.
print.xtable.bpca    Prints \code{xtable.bpca} objects.
qbpca                Evaluates the quality of the biplot representation for
                     \code{bpca.2d} and \code{bpca.3d} objects.
summary.bpca         Summarizes \code{bpca} (\code{bpca.2d} and
                     \code{bpca.3d}) objects.
var.rbf              Calculates the matrix of graphical correlations projected
                     by the biplot for \code{bpca.2d} and \code{bpca.3d}
                     objects.
var.rdf              Calculates the matrix of \dQuote{poor} graphical
                     correlations represented by the biplot for \code{bpca.2d}
                     and \code{bpca.3d}
                     objects.
xtable.bpca          Creates an \code{xtable} method for \code{bpca} objects.

